397    // This is a bit weird. We need to successfully handle these
398    // two cases:
399    // Foo.prototype = new Bar();
400    // and
401    // Foo.prototype = {baz: 3};
402    // In the first case, we do not want new properties to get

718    // form a lattice with the universal constructor at the top of the lattice,
